dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.servicemapping

Interface IRoleBasedPPortAssignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IRoleBasedPPortAssignment
extends IEntity
    IRoleBasedPPortAssignment: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This class specifies an assignment of a role to a particular P-Port. This port must contain a service which is inside of the component and called by outside entity in order to handle a particular issue (e.g. a communication event). This is often named as callback.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
